Subject: drm/syncobj: add missing error return code in
 drm_syncobj_transfer_to_timeline()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f4e3a12bf2d1983b8f352b7719794c52be7e0990
